---
title: Lobster Ravioli in Rosé Sauce with Spinach and Roasted Red Peppers
description: This dish is just the delicious pick-me-up you've been looking for! Lobster ravioli is tossed in a white wine, tomato and cream sauce with roasted red peppers and fennel. Better still, it comes together in no time, so you can treat yourself any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/raviolis-de-homard-a-la-sauce-rosee-e082f331.jpg
